---++ LHC
no big issues. Continuing to attend daily operations meetings; track alarm tickets - test and real; move forward with web services based ticket exchange. 

---++ LIGO
LIGO continuing to run but no big push at the moment to increase the throughput. Robert Engel wrote a very good paper on the errors encountered. Dan Fraser is working to pull lots of different reports of errors encountered together to determine how to communicate the issues to new users so people don't keep having to find the same errors.

---++ Other items
Campus Bridging workshop : Posted the paper from the November workshop to the Work Shop and participated in panel discussions.
